Interface IdentityAPI

All Superinterfaces:
CustomUserInfoAPI, GroupAPI, IdentityAPI, MembershipAPI, OrganizationAPI, RoleAPI, UserAPI
public interface IdentityAPI extends IdentityAPI
This API does not contain anymore anything Subscription-specific. It is here for backwards compatibility. All usable methods come from superinterface IdentityAPI.
Author:
